Since heirlooms and things that could be useful could be sold for some money for daily needs, I started collecting knick-knacks and selling them in online forums.

Pandemic COVID 19 has changed most of the things of us. I have made up my mind to establish a business where women would enjoy more. For some reasons, I started it at emergency store 101.
